headline: Truist Securities Affirms ‘Buy’ Rating on Fiserv (FI), Cuts Price Target
summary: Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE:FI) is one of the best depressed stocks to buy in 2025. On July 29, Truist Securities reiterated a ‘Buy’ rating on the stock but cut its price target to $170 from $185.
